# Infinity Finance â€“ Bank Loan Management System

Infinity Finance is a bank loan management web application designed to provide users with essential loan-related information, EMI calculations, and an admin dashboard for managing loan records.

## ğŸ“š Project Overview

This project is created as part of the TY BBA-CA curriculum at MES Garware College of Commerce, affiliated with Savitribai Phule Pune University. The project focuses on implementing a loan management system using a web-based platform.

## ğŸ’¡ Features

-  Loan Information: Get details about various loan types and eligibility criteria.
-  EMI Calculator: Calculate monthly EMI based on principal amount and tenure.
-  Loan Application Forms: Easy-to-use loan application for customers.
-  Admin Panel: Insert/delete customer loan records and view counters for each loan type.
-  Dashboard: Admin dashboard to track loan applications.
-  FAQs and About Section: Learn more about the institution and general queries.

##  Technologies Used

| Component         | Technology             |
