| Front-end        | HTML, CSS, JavaScript  |
| Back-end         | PHP                    |
| Database         | MySQL                  |


## ğŸ” Admin Features

- View customer applications
- Manage (add/delete) loan entries
- Monitor total applications per loan type

## ğŸ“Œ Limitations

- The loan approval process is offline and involves personal verification, which is not part of the web application.

## âœ… Conclusion

The project successfully delivers a fully functional and user-friendly loan management system. It provides both informational and interactive tools to help users understand loan offerings and apply for them conveniently.


